<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.8.10">
<l>tuṉṉiya pēriruḷ cūḻntu lakaimūṭa</l>
<l>maṉṉiya nāṉmaṟai muṟṟu maṟaintiṭap</l>
<l>piṉṉiv vulakiṉiṟ pēriruḷ nīṅkavaṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṉṉama tāṉāṉē yaccōvaccō</l>
<l rend="indent">vārmaṟai tantāṉē yaccōvaccō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who became that goose that day,</l>
<l rend="indent">when the great darkness that was thick surrounded</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] shrouded the world</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] the eternal four Vedas had completely vanished,</l>
<l>so that the great darkness was afterward dispelled from this world,</l>
<l>Oh! Oh! He who bestowed the precious Vedas! Oh! Oh!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
